beer.beer_description:
Welcome to the Hop Shop! 

Quench your thirst in a sea of aromas ranging from lemon, melon and pineapple. The combination of Citra and Simcoe gives the hazy juice flavours of citrus and stone fruit, while not being overpowering..  Making the beer dangerously sessionable, so watch out!
